vector-skin-desc:
Empu 2 za Vekitoli ziheebwa:
* 2011 - Omulingo omuhyaka gwa MonoKitabu ogwina enzooka empyaka n'enkiza nyingi y'okukozesa.
* 2022 - Vekitoli eyombeka omu kwehinyira kwa WMF [[mw:Desktop Improvements]].
prefs-vector-enable-vector-1-help: Omu myaka mitaito y'okwongeraho, tuliba nitubaziiramu oruhu rwa Vekitoli. Vekitoli y'Ekirale erikwikiriza kurora omulingo omukuru gwa Vekitoli (gw'Okwa ikumi n'abiri 2019). Kwega muno enkora, genda [[mw:Reading/Web/Desktop_Improvements|ha rupapura rw'okwehinyira]] rwaitu.
vector-opt-out-tooltip: Hindura ebikiraanurwa byawe kugaruka ensisana enkuru y'oruhu (Vekitoli y'ekirale)
vector-language-button-aria-label: Genda endugaho omu rudimi rundi. Eroho omu {{PLURAL:$1|rulimi $1|ndimi $1}}
vector-no-language-button-aria-label: Enu endugaho eroho omu rulimi runu rwonka. Taho endugaho omu ndimi ezindi
